1
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,985
[Episode 11: Inspire You]

2
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,597
Help me pick out a dress after school.

3
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,239
No.

4
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:21,441
Yes!

5
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,143
Why me?

6
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,410
Why not Li Nan Xi?

7
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:32,047
Girls and boys have different tastes.

8
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:35,794
I see.

9
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,810
What... do you think?

10
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,947
It's... nice.

11
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,420
So it's not the best.

12
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:11,479
<i>Go, Senior, go!</i>

13
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:13,320
<i>Why do you want the best?</i>

14
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:15,423
<i>You're so fond of Zhong Yi?</i>

15
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:14,960
On purpose?

16
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,847
You made me try on so many outfits.

17
00:03:16,847 --> 00:03:18,844
I don't know what you mean.

18
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:32,062
Dust got into your eyes?

19
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:38,917
Because you didn't select carefully.

20
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,667
I... will.

21
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,432
This one...

22
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,712
looks pretty on you.

23
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,966
<i>This one...</i>

24
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,180
<i>looks pretty on you.</i>

25
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:55,240
What's the noise?

26
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,439
Xi Zhou.

27
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:58,160
Are you up, Xi Zhou?

28
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:00,399
Xi Zhou.

29
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:01,640
Xi Zhou?

30
00:05:40,639 --> 00:05:41,759
In filming,

31
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:44,065
can you meet Chen Xin Hao?

32
00:05:44,065 --> 00:05:45,454
That's not easy.

33
00:05:45,454 --> 00:05:46,680
What about Juan Er?

34
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,160
- Yao Juan Er?
- Yes.

35
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,319
He's more accessible.

36
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:51,279
Who do you usually meet?

37
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:52,678
Qiao Fei.

38
00:05:54,153 --> 00:05:55,160
[Ren Xi Zhou]

39
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,959
<i>Mr. Xiang, I'm lost.</i>

40
00:05:57,959 --> 00:06:00,040
<i>- She's drunk.
- Where am I?</i>

41
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,080
I run a...

42
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,645
I have to go. It's on me.

43
00:06:02,645 --> 00:06:04,280
- Hey, what's the rush?
- Can't we chat longer?

44
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:06,139
- In a hurry?
- Yes.

45
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,040
That punk.

46
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,260
<i>Your Highness.</i>

47
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:24,660
<i>Would you like to ride with me?</i>

48
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:26,879
<i>But...</i>

49
00:06:26,879 --> 00:06:28,974
<i>I'm the sign holder of my class.</i>

50
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,839
<i>- What are you doing?
- Scream.</i>

51
00:06:34,839 --> 00:06:36,520
<i>- None will come to your rescue!
- Let me go!</i>

52
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:37,880
<i>- Let her go!
- What are you doing?</i>

53
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,340
<i>Come back!</i>

54
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,040
<i>Let go!</i>

55
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,436
<i>Let her go!</i>

56
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,189
<i>You...</i>

57
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,997
Why did I have such a dream?

58
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,236
<i>The male and female leads need</i>

59
00:07:35,236 --> 00:07:36,519
<i>a more progressive relationship.</i>

60
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:38,399
<i>Mr. Xiang, please revise it</i>

61
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:39,399
<i>and send it to me ASAP.</i>

62
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:41,155
<i>Okay, I'll.</i>

63
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:02,321
Do you have any water? I'm thirsty.

64
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:15,560
Real natural mineral water,

65
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,981
perfect for me.

66
00:08:16,981 --> 00:08:19,060
I need to supplement micro-elements.

67
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:21,240
Yeah. After a hangover,

68
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:23,080
it's perfect for you to rehydrate.

69
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,560
You could at least explain.

70
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,000
Explain what?

71
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,200
At midnight,

72
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,760
when your ex-girlfriend was drunk,

73
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:54,680
you took her home

74
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:57,609
and changed her clothes without permission!

75
00:09:02,103 --> 00:09:03,480
At midnight,

76
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,600
my ex-girlfriend had a drink with another man,

77
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,120
got drunk,

78
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:09,080
called me to pick her up,

79
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:11,814
and vomited all over me without permission.

80
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:16,000
You knew my address,

81
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,105
but took me home instead!

82
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:22,015
<i>Slowly.</i>

83
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,276
<i>Auntie. Hey.</i>

84
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:32,517
<i>If my mom knows I'm so drunk,</i>

85
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:35,440
<i>she'll kill me!</i>

86
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,802
<i>Let's go!</i>

87
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:47,880
Even if you couldn't send me home,

88
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:49,502
you may as well send me to a hotel.

89
00:09:49,502 --> 00:09:51,280
I asked. It's a peak season.

90
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,520
No vacancy.

91
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,166
Well...

92
00:09:54,166 --> 00:09:57,000
That didn't mean you should
change my clothes without permission.

93
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,746
<i>I can do it!</i>

94
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:10,820
<i>I said I can do it!</i>

95
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,845
<i>Let go of me.</i>

96
00:10:14,519 --> 00:10:16,032
<i>Let go!</i>

97
00:10:17,559 --> 00:10:19,199
<i>I can do it.</i>

98
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:20,999
<i>Get out!</i>

99
00:10:21,652 --> 00:10:22,960
<i>I can do it myself.</i>

100
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:24,395
<i>I can!</i>

101
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,076
That's fine.

102
00:11:32,076 --> 00:11:33,428
That's fine?

103
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,765
Why are you throwing a tantrum?

104
00:11:42,203 --> 00:11:43,240
As an ex,

105
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,960
I won't waste any feelings on you.

106
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,399
That's for the best.

107
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:48,080
But as a friend,

108
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,600
I must warn you

109
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,920
not to get drunk alone,

110
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:54,520
and definitely not with other men.

111
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:58,440
Other men?

112
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:01,055
You mean other men than you?

113
00:12:02,916 --> 00:12:04,039
Go home if you're sober.

114
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:05,240
Answer me first.

115
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:07,432
I'm busy with a storyboard.

116
00:12:07,432 --> 00:12:08,639
Do it quickly.

117
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:09,679
It needs inspiration.

118
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:11,677
Not that easy.

119
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:39,444
<i>Can I hold your hand?</i>

120
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,930
Here.

121
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:04,800
What?

122
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:06,170
Inspiration.

123
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:14,889
Write it.

124
00:13:28,246 --> 00:13:30,720
Where's Ren Xi Zhou?
The opening ceremony is about to start.

125
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,120
Stop, stop!

126
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,731
Where's Ren Xi Zhou?

127
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:41,159
- Hold this.
- What?

128
00:13:41,159 --> 00:13:42,200
You'll be the holder.

129
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:44,720
[Class 3, Grade 10]
Me? I'm not suitable.

130
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,080
Didn't you say you wanted?

131
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:47,280
No!

132
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,720
I have a pimple.

133
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,160
At a distance, none would notice.

134
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:52,240
No. Go away! You go!

135
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:54,520
- You go. You go.
- Here you are.

136
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:55,640
You go.

137
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:57,112
I can go.

138
00:14:03,985 --> 00:14:05,399
Hey. Which class are you in?

139
00:14:05,399 --> 00:14:07,360
My friend wants to add you.
What's your QQ number?

140
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,745
I'm sorry.

141
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:12,640
- Excuse me.
- Okay.

142
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:13,910
Excuse me.

143
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,799
Are you alright?

144
00:14:16,799 --> 00:14:18,120
How's the opening ceremony?

145
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,840
It's... over.

146
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,039
What?

147
00:14:21,039 --> 00:14:22,800
It's over?

148
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:23,960
Yes.

149
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,360
Someone did it for you.

150
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:43,552
So... it's okay.

151
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:49,240
My fault.

152
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,879
Knowing I was to hold it,

153
00:14:50,879 --> 00:14:52,276
I couldn't fall asleep.

154
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:54,000
Wait!

155
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,759
No wonder it looks familiar.

156
00:14:56,759 --> 00:14:59,143
It's our high school story.
